icalendar_light installation
============================


Python ``pip`` package is required to install ``icalendar_light``.


From sources
------------

Use the following command line to install ``icalendar_light`` from sources directory (containing setup.py):

    pip install .

or

    python setup.py install


From PyPI
---------

Alternatively you can install ``icalendar_light`` from PyPI:

    pip install icalendar_light


Use `-U` flag for upgrade:

    pip install -U icalendar_light

